combined_string_full: Arts, Crafts & Sewing. Painting, Drawing & Art Supplies. Shrink wraps. Ingenious crafting fun with the shrink film craft set for young and old With shrink film there are hardly any limits to your creativity  The great properties of the film are ideal for crafting   no matter what you feel like  Why not just buy shrink film and try it out  What is shrink film anyway  The shrinking plastic film is a transparent film that opens after a short warm up in the oven slightly less than half of the original size shrinks  First it curls and bends  then it sinks again and remains wonderfully smooth  Shrinking not only makes the shrink plastic smaller  but also strengthens it and makes it more stable  How is the film used  The films have a smooth and a roughened side  The rough side is actually better for painting because the paint sticks better and therefore covers better  Of course  if you want  you can also paint on the smooth side  After painting  the shrink film simply needs to be cut to size and heated in the oven for 1 2 minutes  Then just take it out  let it cool down and the work of art is ready   Craft tips with shrink plastic   Pay attention to the size  as the film shrinks by approx  50    In principle  any type of pen works  but felt tip pens are particularly suitable for a bright  vibrant result   On the rough side the colors become richer  more even  _  _ig   Which side should be facing down in the oven  In principle it doesn t matter  but we recommend placing the smooth side down for an optimally smooth result You can find these and other products in our craft online shop  Be inspired and browse through our extensive range  You are guaranteed to find more ideas for new craft projects
